    • Picture

      public Picture​(java.lang.String filepath)
      Sets up the metadata information. If the picture cant be processed, or if metadata can't be read, a ImageProcessingException or IOException is thrown in the try/catch-block.
      Parameters:
      filepath - The filepath to the image whose metadata is to be stored.
